					<box></box>
					<textElement textAlignment="Justified">
						<font size="12"/>
					</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[The Family pensioner is informed that if the above amount is found later to be in excess of which he/she is entitled under the rules he/she will be called upon to refund such excess in one lumpsum.

The Family pensioner may be requested to open a Savings Bank Account (not joint/either or survivor account) in any one of the branches of the Bank in which the pension Disbursing Officers is having an account or in any one of the five nationalized banks with whom the Board has banking operations and which is nearest to his residence. The name and address of the Bank along with the Savings Bank Account Number may be intimated to the above Circle Office.

This order is issued subject to recovery of all the dues from the deceased person before settlement of death benefits and if any dues are found to be recoverable from the deceased  person at a later date, the person who furnished the “No Due Certificate” will be held responsible and action will be taken against him and he will be held liable for the unrecovered amount if any.

Please acknowledge the receipt of this order with enclosures and intimate the payment of pension and commutation value with Cheque No. and Date.

]]></text>
				</staticText>
